  &quot;emptyList&quot; : [ ],
  &quot;listOfOne&quot; : [ 1 ],
  &quot;nullSet&quot; : [ ],
  &quot;emptySet&quot; : [ ],
  &quot;setOfOne&quot; : [ &quot;One&quot; ]
}
```
```logs
CollectionsPojo(nullList=null, emptyList=null, listOfOne=[1], nullSet=null, emptySet=null, setOfOne=[One])
